{"tid":1286590,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大公司圍爐，投訴無門，請各路英雄幫忙","createTime":"2019-07-05T02:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T02:33:30.000Z","uid":179712,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34c5eec93a703a8585aa10ebd27585bb2ac3a0d1","tid":1286590,"uid":179712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"李生集團員工，入職大約2年<br />\n因工作上曾直言，被視為挑戰上司<br />\n<br />\n上司從此處處針對，開會時不斷攻擊本人<br />\n<br />\n亦曾多次出言侮辱/中傷本人及家人(有錄音）<br />\n<br />\n因長時間工作令身體出現毛病(尾龍骨因長時間坐移位）睇完醫生後，上司要求我在病假期間工作，交Report比佢(醫療報告，對話紀錄)<br />\n<br />\n被上司長期欺壓同針對，開始有心理壓力，精神出現問題，失眠等症狀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：HR主管同上司官官相衛，曾經同HR溝通該等，被拒絕<br />\n<br />\n小弟英文有限公司<br />\n想寫封英文投訴信比總公司，有人幫到手嗎？<br />\n另外，平機會有用嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72880423476d638efd721ece7764291420cb4836","tid":1286590,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"用武力啦"},{"pid":"25c11a8f25772ced78934f055151e2ef7cb94399","tid":1286590,"uid":52299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"勞工處 同平機會啦"},{"pid":"a9cd8565910eacabe08de3049995812e3febe713","tid":1286590,"uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"好似要開名先有人幫"},{"pid":"fcacc559fe3d303c4d9d85ce94763e087e27662e","tid":1286590,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:27:12.000Z","msg":"有母公司就寫信上去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲忍, 反正最後都係想整走你仲唔玩鋪勁咩"},{"pid":"786fdcde7ff38f283d7d73190364368bd109ce9d","tid":1286590,"uid":179712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9cd8565910eacabe08de3049995812e3febe713","tid":1286590,"uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"好似要開名先有人幫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:31:06.00